### New API Routes

| Route | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/invitations` | GET | Fetch pending in-app invitations for current user |
| `/api/invitations` | POST | Create invitation (JOIN_REQUEST, IN_APP_INVITE, EMAIL_INVITE) |
| `/api/invitations/[id]` | PATCH | Accept or decline an invitation |
| `/api/invitations/count` | GET | Lightweight count for sidebar badge |
| `/api/groups/[id]/invitations` | GET | Fetch pending requests for a group (creator only) |
| `/api/groups/[id]/leave` | POST | Leave a group (sets isActive=false) |
| `/api/groups/[id]/previous` | DELETE | Remove from Previous Groups history |
| `/api/users/search` | GET | Search users by name or userCode |

### Modified API Routes

| Route | Change |
|---|---|
| `/api/groups/join` | Creates JOIN_REQUEST instead of instant join |

